      {
        "frameReference" => "Frames 1-5",
        "painPointTitle" => "Unclear Sign-In Prompt Feedback",
        "severity" => "Medium",
        "issueDescription" => "Violates Nielsen's Heuristic #1: Visibility of System Status. The initial frames show a navigation menu where 'Sign In' is highlighted in place of a more clear prompt. There's no immediate indication that the user needs to sign in for managing projects.",
        "recommendations" => [
          "Add a visible 'Sign In Required' message on areas that require authentication.",
